      <para styleclass="Heading1">Date Type</para>
    </header>
    <para styleclass="Normal">This structure holds year, month, day in 32 bits. For date calculations it uses the System.DateTime calculation logic. There are implicit converters between Date and DateTime.<br/>The internal type name for this type is XSharp.__Date</para>
